Welcome to Static CLDF Demo

This page is designed to query the database locally with SQLite. Data is loaded in memory and can take a while to load. It is intended for experimentation and exploration by advanced users familiar with SQL.

The `sqljs` library is original work by kripken (sql.js), now maintained by lovasoa.


Table schemata:
forms: id text, local_id text, language_id text, parameter_id text, value text, form text, segments text, comment text, source text, cognacy text, loan text
languages: id text, name text, glottocode text, glottolog_name text, iso639p3code text, macroarea text, latitude text, longitude text, family text
parameters: id text, name text, concepticon_id text, concepticon_gloss text, portuguese_gloss text
cognates: id text, form_id text, form text, cognateset_id text, doubt text, cognate_detection_method text, source text, alignment text, alignment_method text, alignment_source text

Results will be displayed here
